# Version Bump Policy

When making code changes in this repository, always bump the cagent version before finishing.

- Update `pyproject.toml` `[project].version`
- Update `src/claude_cli_agent/__init__.py` `__version__`
- If docs mention the expected current version, update those references too

Use a patch bump by default (`0.2.2` -> `0.2.3`) unless the user explicitly asks for minor/major semantics.
